  "description": "This individual is an animate corpse of evident human provenance, reduced to a dry, light-skinned frame with tight, desiccated features and prominent bone structure. Gray eyes sit deep in the sockets beneath a fixed, funerary stare, and black hair persists in an unkempt fall broken by bare patches at the temples. The mouth and jawline show permanent cracking and recession consistent with long exposure to damp, mineral-laden air. The overall aspect is spare and enduring, marked by the resilient rigidity typical of cavern-haunting undead.",
